</li></ul>
</li></ul>
<ul><li> <a href="/Version_2.7" title="Version 2.7">2.7</a>&nbsp;:
<ul><li> Added the <code>link</code> parameter.
</li></ul>
</li></ul>
<ul><li> <a href="/Version_2.5" title="Version 2.5">2.5</a>&nbsp;: 
<ul><li> Added <code>'RAND'</code> order for the <code>order</code> parameter to return tags in a random order.
</li><li> Added <code>'array'</code> format for the <code>format</code> parameter to return an array.
</li></ul>
</li></ul>
